Package bolt.web.coffee.dependency

Interface Summary
DependencyResolver<T extends NamedDependency> An implementation prototype for an object which accepts NamedDependency implementers and provides look-up methods for resolving the added references.
NamedDependency A simple named instance.
 

Class Summary
CoffeeIdentifier This class is used to represent any general coffee-script identifier token, and also a reference to the file it exists in.
CoffeeScriptDependencies This class is used to manage all of the dependencies parsed from the coffee-script source files.
DependencyManager<T extends NamedDependency> This class is just a simple wrapper for a String -> NamedDependency map that implements the DependencyResolver interface for any dependencies referenced prior to creation.
DependencyReference<T extends NamedDependency> Resolves a reference by name using a dependency resolver instance.
DependencyReferenceFactory<T extends NamedDependency>  
OutgoingReferences<T extends NamedDependency> This class tracks a single T instance with a List of DependencyReference instances that represent the outgoing edges for the T instance in the dependency graph.
